{"tid":255620,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港台電視33台下周一起轉播CCTV-1綜合頻道","createTime":"2017-05-24T03:36:35.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-29T15:14:24.000Z","uid":37554,"like":4,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"11ecf47ceca380fbbe3193989193a0c19a108ca0","tid":255620,"uid":37554,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T03:36:35.000Z","msg":"《香港電台約章》訂明港台需要轉播國家電視台的節目。香港電台指出在計劃港台電視33內容之初，曾考慮轉播中央電視台綜合頻道(CCTV-1 綜合)或中央電視台頻道 9 英語紀錄頻道（即現時中國環球電視網紀錄頻道 CGTN Documentary）的節目，惟當時已有本地免費電視台轉播 CCTV-1 綜合的節目，為避免轉播節目重疊播放，因此安排轉播中央電視台頻道9 的節目。<br />\n<br />\n港台解釋現在以上的重疊播放的情況不再存在，又稱絕大多數的香港本地電視觀眾均傾向收看中文電視節目，港台將於本年5月29日起，在港台電視33及33A轉播中央電視台綜合頻道(CCTV-1 綜合)的節目。"},{"pid":"54c49ffb28c3623c20abd23703078b343310410b","tid":255620,"uid":102096,"like":1,"dislike":9,"score":-8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T03:38:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"307a7bd0a087e395a08936f5e9a61c5171b8f287","tid":255620,"uid":41375,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T03:44:00.000Z","msg":"香港都有新聞聯播 與大陸接軌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32e1a5d79e5ffbde7a8c120968403a09a75a6e56","tid":255620,"uid":91604,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T09:29:50.000Z","msg":"播CCTV5啦"},{"pid":"c1299315d1e87c8896e6e40e935e0f1f4cf3db94","tid":255620,"uid":41818,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T09:34:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>終於有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有時d大陸劇仲好睇過無線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />